---
title: Garlic Mushroom Gnocchi (v) with Cavolo Nero and Goat's Cheese
description: Quick, hearty, and packed with delicious flavour, our 20-minute gnocchi is the perfect go-to recipe for busy evenings. Gnocchi, cavolo nero and juicy mushrooms are combined in a velvety creme fraiche sauce before being topped with crumbled goat’s cheese.
